---
layout: base.njk
title: FileZilla 技术文章与教程列表
description: FileZilla FTP 连接、SFTP 传输、站点管理、文件上传与安装配置文章列表。
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-head">
      <h1>FileZilla 技术文章与教程列表</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="list-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="list-card">
          {% if post.data.heroImage %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">
              <img src="{{ post.data.heroImage }}" alt="{{ post.data.heroAlt or post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
            </a>
          {% endif %}
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | readableDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <div class="chip-row">
            {% for tag in post.data.tags | publicTags %}
              <a href="/tags/{{ tag | tagSlug }}/">{{ tag }}</a>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
